    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pick your <strong>coriander</strong> and <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>mint</strong> and <strong>coriander</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> roughly</p>",
