    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>rinsed rice</strong>, <strong>nigella seeds</strong>,<strong> sliced</strong> <strong>cucumber</strong>, <strong>shredded red cabbage </strong>and most of the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and <strong>mint </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to a large bowl</p><p>Squeeze the juice of the <strong>lime[s]</strong> into the bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your<strong> rice salad</strong></p>",
