    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> tandoori basa</strong> over the <strong>rice salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>lime & garlic yoghurt</strong> all over and garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped mint & coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
